definitions.definition: A term of endearment ; Honey , sweetheart
examples: Hey, hon ! How was your day at work?

subdefinitions.definition: ( Southern US ) A friendly term of address .

definitions.definition: ( 4chan /lgbt/ slang , derogatory , offensive ) A trans woman who does not pass ; a clocky trans woman.
examples: This youngshit mogs me: I'm such a hon .
